 has always been at the forefront in contributing towards the society, since the time of its inception. Carrying this legacy forward as a responsible corporate, Rockman has been engaged in various CSR initiatives. The purpose is to introduce a sustainable change in society, especially for the underprivileged and weaker sections.<\/p>\n<div class=\"show_more\">\n<p class=\"wpsm-show\" style=\"color: #ff6f00; font-size: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6f00;\"><strong>Read More &#8230;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<div class=\"wpsm-content wpsm-content-hide\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To institutionalise this initiative, we set up the \u201cROCKMAN FOUNDATION\u201d &#8211; a separate entity to bring more professionals on board and dedicated resources to manage. The foundation primarily focuses on CSR initiative under \u201cMISSION PARIVARTAN\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>Mission Parivartan started in the year 2014 to inspire and commit people towards the changing society, in association with a professional organisation Mrida. New initiatives did well and brought changes in the community on three fronts; Health, Education and Employability. This model and induction of Mirda have given us lots of experience and knowledge and opportunities for direct involvement in the project along with villagers.<\/p>\n<p>The aim is to help and improve the underprivileged Society through advancement in:<\/p>\n<p class=\"wpsm-hide\" style=\"color: #ff6f00; font-size: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6f00;\"><strong>Read Less &#8230;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/6&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#82